  "session": "2026RS",
  "identifier": "HB 43",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to deputy coroner training.",
  "abstract": "Amend KRS 72.415 to allow the commissioner of the Department of Criminal Justice Training  to grant an extension to a deputy coroner to complete the required training; specify when the extension begins to toll; specify consequences for failure to complete the training within the time period of the extension; delete provisions relating to reinstatement and pay modification of deputy coroners who fail to complete the required training.",
